.mk'`.\n\n---\n\n`P` is local at the target if\n1. `P` respects isomorphisms.\n2. If `P` holds for `f : X ⟶ Y`, then `P` holds for `f ∣_ U` for any `U`.\n3. If `P` holds for `f ∣_ U` for an open cover `U` of `Y`, then `P` holds for `f`.\n","docLink":"./Mathlib/AlgebraicGeometry/Morphisms/Basic.html#AlgebraicGeometry.IsLocalAtTarget.mk'","kind":"theorem","line":676,"name":"AlgebraicGeometry.IsLocalAtTarget.mk'","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/087469e24922b85cb737497c74556c7dacc01f22/Mathlib/AlgebraicGeometry/Morphisms/Basic.lean#L676-L677"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/AlgebraicGeometry/Morphisms/Basic.html#AlgebraicGeometry.IsLocalAtTarget\"><span class=\"name\">AlgebraicGeometry</span>.<span class=\"name\">IsLocalAtTarget</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">P</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/MorphismProperty/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.MorphismProperty\">CategoryTheory.MorphismProperty</a> <a href=\"./Mathlib/AlgebraicGeometry/Scheme.html#AlgebraicGeometry.Scheme\">Scheme</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Prop</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"**Alias** of `AlgebraicGeometry.IsZariskiLocalAtTarget`.\n\n---\n\nA property is Zariski-local at target if it is local at target in the Zariski topology. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/AlgebraicGeometry/Morphisms/Basic.html#AlgebraicGeometry.IsLocalAtTarget","kind":"def","line":672,"name":"AlgebraicGeometry.IsLocalAtTarget","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/087469e24922b85cb737497c74556c7dacc01f22/Mathlib/AlgebraicGeometry/Morphisms/Basic.lean#L672-L672"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">instance</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" 